The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of disentangled variational representation and optimization techniques suggest that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves the use of correlation alignment and identity information, which are common concepts in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
